We are beyond excited to announce the GRAND OPENING of Jeevee Square in Baneshwor—a 10,000 sq. ft. space designed to revolutionize your shopping experience! 🎉
This milestone marks a significant new chapter for SALT as we extend our commitment to delivering a delightful shopping experience, now with our 3rd outlet for SALT and 2nd for Aadhya and 3 New Fashion Brands, curated by The house of SALT. 
From skincare and makeup to Gen Z fashion, ethnic apparel, baby products, and toys, Jeevee Square brings together everything you need under one roof. On our very first day itself, we had the privilege of welcoming over 3,000+ visitors, and the energy was truly inspiring!
We invite you to visit us in-store to discover it all first hand.
Here’s what awaits you at Jeevee Square:
✨ Jeeveelush: A one-stop destination with over 200+ beauty brands and FREE skincare testing to find the perfect products for your skin! 
👶 Jeeveebees: A delightful selection of over 2000+ baby apparels, toys, and products designed to inspire creativity and joy in your little ones.
👗 SALT: Proudly introducing our 3rd exclusive outlet, offering the widest selection for our fashion-forward shoppers!
🏃🏽‍♀️‍➡️SALT Active: launching for the first time at Baneshwor, the active wear Collection from SALT. 
🧥 Aadhya & Rang: Discover ethnic wear across a range of styles and prices to suit every occasion.
👕 Wasabi: Excited to launch our first-ever outlet, featuring a curated collection of Gen Z fashion.
🎀 Pepper: Debuting with a fabulous collection of trendy accessories and more cute finds.

latestPosts.caption:
I’m back to the exact weight I was on the day I found out I was pregnant , not toned and fit as before but a milestone worth sharing!

After delivery, I started working out 8 weeks postpartum, with my doctor’s guidance. I stayed committed to eating healthy, continued breastfeeding, and remained mindful of my food choices. Consistent workouts and stretching not only helped me reach my weight goal, but also supported my physical recovery and kept my mind refreshed.

Now, I’m shifting focus to building strength, improving mobility, and adding a little toning. I’m truly enjoying this journey mind, body, and soul. 💪✨
